text: The Unknown Terror is a 1957 American science fiction horror movie. It was directed by Charles Marquis Warren. Actors include John Howard, Mala Powers, Paul Richards, and May Wynn. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1957 horror movies Category:1957 science fiction movies Category:American science fiction horror movies Category:Movies directed by Charles Marquis Warren
